data.description: Escape to your own desert paradise in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1,568 sq ft home nestled on 2.31 acres of pristine land. With unobstructed desert views, this property is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, offering quick access to iconic destinations like Goat Mountain, Joshua Tree National Monument (18 miles away), and Big Bear (53 miles away). Inside, you'll find an inviting kitchen, a spacious master bedroom with a private bathroom and walk-in closet, a beautiful Fireplace in family area, and a convenient laundry area. This secluded oasis provides tranquility and breathtaking sunrises and sunsets, making it a rare opportunity to own a slice of desert heaven. Don't miss out – call today for a viewing!
